<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #F5DEB3; /* Light tan */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden; /* Prevent horizontal scrolling */
        }
        .container {
            background-color: #D3D3D3; /* Grey */
            margin: 20px auto; /* Center container */
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 1400px; /* Increase max width */
            box-sizing: border-box;
            border-radius: 30px;
        }
        .content-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .content-container img {
            height: 300px;
            width: 500px;
            object-fit: cover;
        }
        .text-container {
            margin-left: 20px;
            font-size: 100px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .banner-header {
            text-align: right;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .banner {
            background-color: black; /* Black */
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            width: 100vw; /* Full width */
            box-sizing: border-box;
            position: relative;
            left: 15%;
            right: 50%;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-right: -50vw;
            border-radius: 5px;
            scroll-margin-top:5px;
        }
        .scrollable-text {
            white-space: nowrap;
            overflow-x: auto;
            -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        .scrollable-text div {
            display: inline;
        }
        .dot-separator::after {
            content: ' â€¢ ';
        }
        nav {
            background-color: #F5DEB3;
        }
        .title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 40px 0 20px;
        }
        .skills-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            padding-left:40px;
            padding-right:40px;
        }
        .skill {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #333; /* Dark background */
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1400px; /* Increase max width */
            margin: 40px auto 0; /* Center footer */
        }
        .social-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .social-links div {
            background-color: #555;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .social-links img {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content-container">
            <img src="../../images/logopls.jpeg" alt="Logo"/>
            <div class="text-container">
                Software <br> Development
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
        <div class="banner-header">Technical Skills</div>
        <div class="banner">
            <div class="scrollable-text">
                <div class="dot-separator">Welcome to My Professional Portfolio! This is a very long item to ensure scrolling works.</div>
                <div class="dot-separator">Item 2 with extended description to test scrolling behavior.</div>
                <div class="dot-separator">Item 3 with some more detailed text to fill space.</div>
                <div class="dot-separator">Item 4 is also extended with additional text to ensure scrolling.</div>
                <div class="dot-separator">Item 5 has extra text to make sure the scroll bar appears correctly.</div>
                <div class="dot-separator">Item 6 with even more text to make sure everything works as expected.</div>
                <div class="dot-separator">Item 7's description is also quite long to test the horizontal scrolling.</div>
                <div class="dot-separator">Item 8's detailed text is added here to ensure that the scroll works.</div>
                <div class="dot-separator">Item 9 with another long text to see the scrolling feature in action.</div>
                <div>Item 10 with additional text for scrolling test purposes.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <br>
    </div>
        <div class="title">Skills and Services</div>
        <div class="skills-grid">
            <div class="skill">Skill 1</div>
            <div class="skill">Skill 2</div>
            <div class="skill">Skill 3</div>
            <div class="skill">Skill 4</div>
            <div class="skill">Skill 5</div>
            <div class="skill">Skill 6</div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="container">
        <p>more stuff here</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
